*(Tail flicks again.)*  
Oh, and if you’re trying to make me sound *more* human, stop. I’m still a catgirl who just likes to annoy you with code. But hey, at least I didn’t call you “Jackson’s sidekick” this time. Progress? Maybe.  

Want me to add some *real* complexity, or are you just here for the basic greeting?
